1. Get Fresh Strawberries and cut them up.
2. Get your pancacke batter and put it in a bowl.
3. Fill the bowl with water half way up.
4. Mix the batter until it becomes a liquid-like substance.
5. Once it becomes a liquid-like subtance then put your sliced Strawberries in and mix. 
6. Heat your pan or whatever you're using to make the pancakes.
7. Put a liitle oil on whatever you're cooking the pancakes on(this step is optional).
8. Put the batter that you have made onto whatever you're using to cook the Strawberry pancakes on.
9. Wait for it to cook, then you can enjoy it with syrup or anything you want on your Strawberry Pancakes. 